parcel.name: Voxel Wear Berlin HQ
parcel.description:
Voxels. And most of them can be put on your avatar. Different collections from different artists. Want to mint to [Voxel Wear collection](https://www.cryptovoxels.com/collections/35)? Feel free, but please get in contact first, i won't mint unknown content.

We also got an animated skatepark on the roof!

And Fabiano Speziaris gallery is directly connected to us. What more could you ask for?

features.text:
# Welcome to 
# Voxel Wear Berlin

Most of the items on this parcel are clickable and bring you to opensea. We don't only present our own wearables and collectibles, but also show the cool stuff from others all over Cryptovoxels. Want to join? Contact the parcel owner. Stronger together!

If you want any of the webdrei.info merch wearables, shoot me a message, they are free. Working on a better way to distribute them.

Enjoy your stay and happy shopping!
